34d3320d50e890a68aea8cb2f2a8fd7464f","tid":253963,"uid":11724,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-22T21:43:36.000Z","msg":"有，好似chronicle咁"},{"pid":"3774f6c786abfddcce9502c2d53b941128ab3393","tid":253963,"uid":17232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-22T21:53:18.000Z","msg":"前日就發左個識飛既夢，覺得好難控制。有一下我係想向下飛少少，但係唔小心一野衝左落地下。"},{"pid":"4524554aae56f683745740d1bd8693bb20e1c3a9","tid":253963,"uid":22580,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-22T21:58:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>前日就發左個識飛既夢，覺得好難控制。有一下我係想向下飛少少，但係唔小心一野衝左落地下。</blockquote><br />\n我係突然冇風跟住跌左落地下<br />\n膝頭好痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9bb02dcf6084a7cbc5f48efd249c7d8fd4f77753","tid":253963,"uid":8345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-22T21:59:45.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"61dc6d9ea22adbc466c3d16a522f2c6f008d345e","tid":253963,"uid":17232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-22T22:08:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>前日就發左個識飛既夢，覺得好難控制。有一下我係想向下飛少少，但係唔小心一野衝左落地下。</blockquote><br />\n我係突然冇風跟住跌左落地下<br />\n膝頭好痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n發夢會痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ？<br />\n不過我完全唔係飄，亦都無翼，而真係好似浮起身咁。"},{"pid":"d2da9c2ff0c041590e37df8f3fc413da5b492282","tid":253963,"uid":83798,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T19:18:35.000Z","msg":"我係發夢用掃把飛，意識到比人追緊就好難飛起<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我都想控制個夢呀，冇成功過囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/19.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}